  <T n="perk_description">0xDD93C8D<!--<font color = '#bc0f0f'>The Ultimate Curse!</font>\n\n<b>Requires</b> a Ghost Mastery of <b>Transcendent Wraith</b> to use.\nPerform <font color = '#bc0f0f'>Evil Abilities</font> to fill the meter to <b>unlock</b> this!\n\nUnleash vengeance upon unsuspecting living Sims by casting a malevolent curse upon them. Things just tend to go wrong and everyday tasks become a burden for Sims who are inflicted with the Ultimate Curse. As a haunting bonus, this ability unlocks the <b>'Mark of Evil'</b>, a tattoo available exclusively for the most malicious ghosts.\n\nThe <b>Mark of Evil tattoo</b> is available in Create a Sim or can be applied directly as a self-interaction.\n\nPerforming the interaction grants <font color = '#bc0f0f'>Fear Essence</font>.--></T>
